1
00:00:06,070 --> 00:00:08,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's have a flower-viewing party!</font>

2
00:00:09,120 --> 00:00:10,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's do it!</font>

3
00:00:10,910 --> 00:00:15,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This morning, I saw a spot 
where they were in full bloom!</font>

4
00:00:15,240 --> 00:00:16,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's all go see them together!</font>

5
00:00:16,870 --> 00:00:17,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

6
00:00:17,950 --> 00:00:20,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It doesn't really do us any good to
 look at some cherry blossoms.</font>

7
00:00:20,830 --> 00:00:22,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And it'll be all dusty.</font>

8
00:00:22,870 --> 00:00:25,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, that's true.</font>

9
00:00:25,960 --> 00:00:27,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What a shame.</font>

10
00:00:30,200 --> 00:00:31,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I guess we could go.</font>

11
00:00:31,460 --> 00:00:33,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I do happen to be free tonight.</font>

12
00:00:33,260 --> 00:00:35,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you!</font>

13
00:00:35,180 --> 00:00:37,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not quite satisfied 
with how this went...</font>

14
00:00:37,720 --> 00:00:40,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But whatever! Let's go!</font>

15
00:00:40,360 --> 00:00:42,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All right!</font>

16
00:00:43,960 --> 00:00:47,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Siu-san, have you ever been 
to a flower-viewing party?</font>

17
00:00:47,180 --> 00:00:50,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do I look like a man who likes flowers?</font>

18
00:00:50,120 --> 00:00:51,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, very much so.</font>

19
00:00:51,680 --> 00:00:53,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't just say random shit.</font>

20
00:00:54,130 --> 00:00:55,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Papa, cherry blossoms!</font>

21
00:00:54,320 --> 00:00:56,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I didn't really look at the flowers,</font>

22
00:00:55,510 --> 00:00:56,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Yes, they are.</font>

23
00:00:56,870 --> 00:00:58,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Papa, they're pretty!</font>

24
00:00:57,330 --> 00:00:59,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but my kids pestered me, so we went.</font>

25
00:00:58,520 --> 00:00:59,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Yes, they are.</font>

26
00:01:02,520 --> 00:01:03,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That makes sense.</font>

27
00:01:05,840 --> 00:01:08,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Flower viewing! Flower viewing!</font>

28
00:01:08,730 --> 00:01:11,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's go! Let's go!</font>

29
00:01:09,100 --> 00:01:10,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't wait.</font>

30
00:01:11,640 --> 00:01:14,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, Hugh, do you like 
flower-viewing parties?</font>

31
00:01:15,060 --> 00:01:16,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not sure.</font>

32
00:01:16,300 --> 00:01:18,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've only ever done them as a child.</font>

33
00:01:18,880 --> 00:01:20,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Same here.</font>

34
00:01:20,650 --> 00:01:23,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wasn't particularly into them before...</font>

35
00:01:24,260 --> 00:01:27,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but when I saw them today, 
they were so pretty.</font>

36
00:01:28,850 --> 00:01:32,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And I thought, "It'd be so nice 
to look at them with everyone."</font>

37
00:01:34,030 --> 00:01:36,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I thought the same thing!</font>

38
00:01:36,550 --> 00:01:39,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Really? So we're the same!</font>

39
00:01:41,580 --> 00:01:43,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't wait to go!</font>

40
00:01:43,540 --> 00:01:44,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah!</font>

41
00:01:46,310 --> 00:01:47,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A flower-viewing party?</font>

42
00:01:48,000 --> 00:01:50,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Apparently, they're going 
after they finish work.</font>

43
00:01:50,340 --> 00:01:53,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, yes. Well, they will 
fall soon, after all.</font>

44
00:01:54,730 --> 00:01:55,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you want to go, too?</font>

45
00:01:55,930 --> 00:01:58,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, I'm not interested.</font>

46
00:01:58,580 --> 00:02:02,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I'm glad everyone
is getting along so well.</font>

47
00:02:02,560 --> 00:02:04,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're such good kids, aren't they?</font>

48
00:02:04,600 --> 00:02:07,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'd love to see the 
people who raised them!</font>

49
00:02:08,510 --> 00:02:10,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shall I bring you a mirror?</font>

50
00:03:39,070 --> 00:03:43,160
<font size="20" color="#000000">{\an8}<b><font size="35"><font color="#171719">The <font color="#d9000d">Daily <font color="#269df2">L<font color="#171719">ife of a <font color="#ef670f">P<font color="#171719">art-Time <font color="#44c10c">T<font color="#171719">orturer</font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></b></font>

51
00:03:48,740 --> 00:03:51,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Gloom...</font>

52
00:03:48,790 --> 00:03:51,210
<font size="20" color="#000000"><b><font face="Comic Sans MS"><font color="#1c161f"><font size="25">GLOOM</font></font></font></b></font>

53
00:03:51,380 --> 00:03:54,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">With this much work, 
we won't have time for a flower viewing.</font>

54
00:03:54,160 --> 00:03:55,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Boo.</font>

55
00:03:55,670 --> 00:03:57,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't act like babies.</font>

56
00:03:57,420 --> 00:03:59,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry.</font>

57
00:03:59,040 --> 00:04:01,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's not like this is your fault.</font>

58
00:04:01,100 --> 00:04:03,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We got some urgent cases in,</font>

59
00:04:03,500 --> 00:04:05,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but Siu-san and I will handle them.</font>

60
00:04:06,330 --> 00:04:07,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You two can go if you want.</font>

61
00:04:10,180 --> 00:04:11,600
<font size="20" color="#000000"><font face="Comic Sans MS"><b><font color="#33263a">HISS</font></b></font></font>

62
00:04:12,000 --> 00:04:15,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wanted to see them 
with all of us together.</font>

63
00:04:15,920 --> 00:04:19,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If just the two of us go, 
there's no point.</font>

64
00:04:19,240 --> 00:04:20,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mike-kun...</font>

65
00:04:22,370 --> 00:04:26,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But... I understand how 
important this work is.</font>

66
00:04:27,610 --> 00:04:29,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So let's do our best 
and get it all wrapped up!</font>

67
00:04:29,800 --> 00:04:30,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah!</font>

68
00:04:31,300 --> 00:04:32,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Seriously...</font>

69
00:04:33,260 --> 00:04:35,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You've become such good kids!</font>

70
00:04:35,330 --> 00:04:38,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I guess your big brother here will 
have to show what he can really do.</font>

71
00:04:38,290 --> 00:04:40,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right, Papa?</font>

72
00:04:40,010 --> 00:04:41,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who're you calling "Papa"?</font>

73
00:04:44,470 --> 00:04:47,220
<font size="20" color="#000000"><b><font color="#f1f1f1">Done</font></b></font>

74
00:04:46,010 --> 00:04:47,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That was fast!</font>

75
00:04:47,860 --> 00:04:49,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We did hurry, but...</font>

76
00:04:49,540 --> 00:04:51,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">if we change clothes, 
we won't make it in time.</font>

77
00:04:51,680 --> 00:04:54,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's pitch-black over there at night.</font>

78
00:04:55,160 --> 00:04:56,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh.</font>

79
00:04:56,020 --> 00:04:59,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's a cherry tree at the 
park near here, isn't there?</font>

80
00:04:59,480 --> 00:05:01,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The one that has the 
street lights on at night.</font>

81
00:05:01,740 --> 00:05:03,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's go there!</font>

82
00:05:03,590 --> 00:05:06,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It won't be much compared 
to the place you wanted to go.</font>

83
00:05:06,120 --> 00:05:07,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's totally fine!</font>

84
00:05:07,900 --> 00:05:09,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's try going there.</font>

85
00:05:14,920 --> 00:05:16,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's so pretty.</font>

86
00:05:16,940 --> 00:05:19,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">One tree is more than enough!</font>

87
00:05:19,400 --> 00:05:21,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, cherry blossoms 
are cherry blossoms.</font>

88
00:05:21,390 --> 00:05:23,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, they're quite impressive.</font>

89
00:05:24,320 --> 00:05:26,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, good work again today!</font>

90
00:05:27,070 --> 00:05:28,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cheers!</font>

91
00:05:33,700 --> 00:05:34,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you...</font>

92
00:05:35,330 --> 00:05:38,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">you for going along with
our selfish request today.</font>

93
00:05:38,980 --> 00:05:40,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's not a problem.</font>

94
00:05:40,420 --> 00:05:42,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mike-chan, are you satisfied, too?</font>

95
00:05:42,560 --> 00:05:45,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes! Thank you.</font>

96
00:05:45,920 --> 00:05:48,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'd like to see them with 
everyone again sometime.</font>

97
00:05:54,920 --> 00:05:56,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah.</font>

98
00:06:06,480 --> 00:06:09,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Welcome, everyone!</font>

99
00:06:09,680 --> 00:06:13,100
<font size="20" color="#000000"><b><font face="Comic Sans MS"><font color="#f9fafc">THRILLED</font></font></b></font>

100
00:06:09,840 --> 00:06:13,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We've been wanting to 
come here for so long!</font>

101
00:06:13,090 --> 00:06:15,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can look around the first 
floor without a license,</font>

102
00:06:15,700 --> 00:06:18,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so you could've come sooner!</font>

103
00:06:18,430 --> 00:06:20,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's what I thought,</font>

104
00:06:20,540 --> 00:06:22,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but Siu-san and Sero-san said...</font>

105
00:06:24,060 --> 00:06:27,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"If you go by yourselves, 
you'll be sitting ducks, so don't do it."</font>

106
00:06:27,880 --> 00:06:30,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-I wouldn't take advantage of you!</font>

107
00:06:31,720 --> 00:06:32,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wow!</font>

108
00:06:32,950 --> 00:06:35,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There are so many books 
I've never seen before!</font>

109
00:06:35,920 --> 00:06:37,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wow, this is incredible!</font>

110
00:06:38,190 --> 00:06:41,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There are specialist volumes here 
that aren't in general circulation.</font>

111
00:06:41,710 --> 00:06:44,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're all pretty expensive.</font>

112
00:06:44,350 --> 00:06:46,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Makes it hard to decide which to buy.</font>

113
00:06:46,940 --> 00:06:48,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you deciding between?</font>

114
00:06:52,170 --> 00:06:53,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll take all of them.</font>

115
00:06:54,010 --> 00:06:55,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're big brother sitting ducks.</font>

116
00:06:57,020 --> 00:06:58,930
<font size="20" color="#000000"><b>{\an8}<font color="#191919"><font size="18">Torture Supply Store
 2nd Floor</font></font></b></font>

117
00:06:59,590 --> 00:07:01,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your licenses look okay.</font>

118
00:07:01,840 --> 00:07:04,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You and your companions 
can come right this way!</font>

119
00:07:06,960 --> 00:07:08,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is amazing!</font>

120
00:07:08,670 --> 00:07:09,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right?</font>

121
00:07:09,550 --> 00:07:11,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Look! Look at this device!</font>

122
00:07:09,560 --> 00:07:12,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who gets that excited in 
a shop like this? Weirdos.</font>

123
00:07:11,440 --> 00:07:13,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Wow, that's so cool!</font>

124
00:07:12,990 --> 00:07:15,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's a new model of whip out.</font>

125
00:07:19,430 --> 00:07:22,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Siu-san... you're pretty odd yourself.</i></font>

126
00:07:25,160 --> 00:07:27,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's a garrote! Wow!</font>

127
00:07:27,820 --> 00:07:29,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's so cool!</font>

128
00:07:30,910 --> 00:07:32,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Excuse me, Belta-san?</font>

129
00:07:32,640 --> 00:07:34,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hmm? What is it?</font>

130
00:07:34,130 --> 00:07:36,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Would you mind taking a picture of us?</font>

131
00:07:36,690 --> 00:07:37,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

132
00:07:36,690 --> 00:07:38,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Peace! Peace!</font>

133
00:07:40,810 --> 00:07:44,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I like how it's so easy to adjust 
the pressure on the neck.</font>

134
00:07:44,930 --> 00:07:47,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It steadily inflicts pain and fear,</font>

135
00:07:47,800 --> 00:07:49,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so it'd make it easy 
to extract information!</font>

136
00:07:50,470 --> 00:07:53,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I get a lot of odd ones 
among my customers...</font>

137
00:07:53,500 --> 00:07:55,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but those kids are way weirder than most.</font>

138
00:07:55,960 --> 00:07:57,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, I thought they might be.</font>

139
00:07:57,860 --> 00:07:59,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're very promising, after all.</font>

140
00:08:02,900 --> 00:08:05,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How do you use this?</font>

141
00:08:05,270 --> 00:08:06,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, that?</font>

142
00:08:06,590 --> 00:08:08,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's like a crane game.</font>

143
00:08:08,250 --> 00:08:10,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It grabs onto flesh or skin.</font>

144
00:08:10,400 --> 00:08:12,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Like... Wham!</font>

145
00:08:12,280 --> 00:08:13,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Seems painful.</font>

146
00:08:13,530 --> 00:08:15,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do we have one?</font>

147
00:08:15,600 --> 00:08:18,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It's so funny how their 
tastes are slightly different.</i></font>

148
00:08:20,280 --> 00:08:22,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A license, huh?</font>

149
00:08:22,320 --> 00:08:24,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Maybe I'll try studying for one.</font>

150
00:08:24,910 --> 00:08:27,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It never hurts to have one.</font>

151
00:08:27,100 --> 00:08:29,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you're going to get one, 
I'll give you some gentle lessons.</font>

152
00:08:29,710 --> 00:08:31,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just give it some thought.</font>

153
00:08:31,530 --> 00:08:33,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We will!</font>

154
00:08:33,400 --> 00:08:35,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Gentle, huh?</font>

155
00:08:35,870 --> 00:08:39,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He wasn't gentle with me at all!</i></font>

156
00:08:39,920 --> 00:08:42,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Because I believed 
in you, obviously.</font>

157
00:08:43,760 --> 00:08:44,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Siu-san!</font>

158
00:08:44,850 --> 00:08:46,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't force me to do this dumb stuff.</font>

159
00:08:48,150 --> 00:08:49,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So, that's what this shop is like.</font>

160
00:08:49,960 --> 00:08:51,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you feel satisfied?</font>

161
00:08:51,140 --> 00:08:51,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes!</font>

162
00:08:52,360 --> 00:08:54,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you want to come again, just ask.</font>

163
00:08:54,170 --> 00:08:55,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sero-san!</font>

164
00:08:55,580 --> 00:08:58,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can we get a garrote at our place?</font>

165
00:08:58,320 --> 00:09:00,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I guess I could ask Noe.</font>

166
00:09:00,150 --> 00:09:02,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If that doesn't work, 
just cry until he caves.</font>

167
00:09:02,170 --> 00:09:02,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, sir!</font>

168
00:09:02,890 --> 00:09:03,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, right.</font>

169
00:09:03,960 --> 00:09:06,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Bel-san, are they finished?</font>

170
00:09:06,990 --> 00:09:09,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They've already arrived!</font>

171
00:09:11,020 --> 00:09:12,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait here just a sec, okay?</font>

172
00:09:20,230 --> 00:09:22,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Those are presents from us.</font>

173
00:09:23,070 --> 00:09:24,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sero-san!</font>

174
00:09:24,980 --> 00:09:26,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mike-chan, put it down. Put it down.</font>

175
00:09:25,530 --> 00:09:26,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sero-san!</font>

176
00:09:27,960 --> 00:09:29,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wow! This is amazing!</font>

177
00:09:28,310 --> 00:09:29,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's incredible!</font>

178
00:09:29,820 --> 00:09:32,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It has my name on it!</font>

179
00:09:32,080 --> 00:09:33,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mine has mine, too!</font>

180
00:09:33,380 --> 00:09:35,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's use these and work even harder!</font>

181
00:09:35,940 --> 00:09:36,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah!</font>

182
00:09:37,520 --> 00:09:39,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It just took one device</font>

183
00:09:39,510 --> 00:09:41,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">to get them that motivated.</font>

184
00:09:42,000 --> 00:09:44,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Those were good purchases, huh?</font>

185
00:09:44,000 --> 00:09:45,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Actually, though...</font>

186
00:09:45,970 --> 00:09:49,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're just so cute that we 
wanted to reward them, that's all.</font>

187
00:09:49,630 --> 00:09:51,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's all it was.</font>

188
00:09:51,330 --> 00:09:54,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Forget love-blinded parents. 
They're love-blinded mentors.</i></font>

189
00:09:57,830 --> 00:09:59,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're off to do some torturing!</font>

190
00:09:59,870 --> 00:10:01,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey!</font>

191
00:10:01,320 --> 00:10:03,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you using those again?</font>

192
00:10:03,550 --> 00:10:04,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes.</font>

193
00:10:05,230 --> 00:10:08,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's no need to use those 
for everything, you know.</font>

194
00:10:08,310 --> 00:10:10,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But...</font>

195
00:10:10,300 --> 00:10:12,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No buts!</font>

196
00:10:12,150 --> 00:10:14,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you're going to act spoiled, 
I'll take them away!</font>

197
00:10:14,390 --> 00:10:16,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?!</font>

198
00:10:16,000 --> 00:10:18,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Keep it to twice a day.</font>

199
00:10:20,480 --> 00:10:21,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you their mom?</font>

200
00:10:21,970 --> 00:10:24,970
<font size="20" color="#000000">{\an8}<b><font size="35"><font color="#fefefe">The <font color="#c5b9cc">D<font color="#fefefe">aily <font color="#c5b9cc">L<font color="#fefefe">ife of a <font color="#625366">P<font color="#fefefe">art-Time <font color="#625366">T<font color="#fefefe">orturer</font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></b></font>

201
00:10:24,970 --> 00:10:27,980
<font size="20" color="#000000">{\an8}<b><font size="35"><font color="#0b0a0c">The <font color="#36c4a4">D<font color="#0b0a0c">aily <font color="#991bea">L<font color="#0b0a0c">ife of a <font color="#f0a62f">P<font color="#0b0a0c">art-Time <font color="#53d336">T<font color="#0b0a0c">orturer</font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></b></font>

202
00:10:32,200 --> 00:10:33,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hiya!</font>

203
00:10:33,870 --> 00:10:36,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've come again today 
to pick up the dregs!</font>

204
00:10:36,850 --> 00:10:38,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you all happily torturing...</font>

205
00:10:38,920 --> 00:10:40,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can see you're not.</font>

206
00:10:39,240 --> 00:10:41,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Sob, sob...</font>

207
00:10:40,440 --> 00:10:41,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's wrong?</font>

208
00:10:42,110 --> 00:10:44,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't get so sad.</font>

209
00:10:44,570 --> 00:10:47,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can't change what's already been done.</font>

210
00:10:47,200 --> 00:10:48,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sero-san...</font>

211
00:10:48,690 --> 00:10:50,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, what happened?</font>

212
00:10:50,540 --> 00:10:52,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It was pretty much fine 
if that one died anyway.</font>

213
00:10:51,130 --> 00:10:55,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Um, hey. What happened?</font>

214
00:10:55,880 --> 00:10:58,010
<font size="20" color="#000000"><b><font color="#353037">Safety First</font></b></font>

215
00:10:55,880 --> 00:10:58,010
<font size="20" color="#000000"><b><font color="#97363f">Let's stay safe today!</font></b></font>

216
00:10:56,890 --> 00:10:58,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, dear.</font>

217
00:10:58,400 --> 00:11:01,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You let someone die 
who wasn't a korokke?</font>

218
00:11:01,510 --> 00:11:04,720
<font size="20" color="#000000"><font face="Comic Sans MS"><b><font color="#f5f5f5"><font size="23">Korokke
</font></font></b><font size="18">A target it's okay to kill</font></font></font>

219
00:11:03,190 --> 00:11:04,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's right.</font>

220
00:11:04,720 --> 00:11:07,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's the one you were 
scheduled to take today.</font>

221
00:11:07,870 --> 00:11:10,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, that one? 
I'm sure it'll be fine, then.</font>

222
00:11:10,600 --> 00:11:12,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right?</font>

223
00:11:12,200 --> 00:11:15,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wh-What if we killed 
someone and it wasn't okay?</font>

224
00:11:15,840 --> 00:11:17,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What would happen to us?</font>

225
00:11:17,900 --> 00:11:22,990
<font size="20" color="#000000"><b><font face="Impact"><font color="#241c26">License 
Revoked</font></font></b></font>

226
00:11:17,900 --> 00:11:20,700
<font size="20" color="#000000"><b><font face="Impact"><font color="#241c26">Disbarred</font></font></b></font>

227
00:11:18,360 --> 00:11:20,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your license would be revoked.</font>

228
00:11:20,650 --> 00:11:22,990
<font size="20" color="#000000"><b><font face="Impact"><font color="#241c26">Fined</font></font></b></font>

229
00:11:20,850 --> 00:11:23,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And the company would get fined.</font>

230
00:11:23,160 --> 00:11:25,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's an unexpectedly normal response.</font>

231
00:11:26,120 --> 00:11:27,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">To put it simply,</font>

232
00:11:27,740 --> 00:11:30,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">korokke cases are ones that 
are low on the priority list.</font>

233
00:11:30,710 --> 00:11:37,120
<font size="20" color="#000000"><b><font size="18"><font color="#2f212c">(Worth as a Source of Information)</font></font></b></font>

234
00:11:30,870 --> 00:11:37,920
<font size="20" color="#000000"><b><font size="11"><font color="#22171c">Must Keep Alive</font></font></b></font>

235
00:11:30,910 --> 00:11:37,920
<font size="20" color="#000000"><b><font size="11"><font color="#22171c">Unavoidable Death</font></font></b></font>

236
00:11:31,040 --> 00:11:33,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The scale and number of 
the crimes they've committed,</font>

237
00:11:31,080 --> 00:11:37,920
<font size="20" color="#000000"><b><font size="15"><font color="#1f1f32">Possibly Unnecessary</font></font></b></font>

238
00:11:32,330 --> 00:11:37,920
<font size="20" color="#000000"><b><font size="15"><font color="#1f1f32">Adequate</font></font></b></font>

239
00:11:33,330 --> 00:11:37,920
<font size="20" color="#000000"><b><font size="15"><font color="#1f1f32">Not Bad</font></font></b></font>

240
00:11:33,710 --> 00:11:35,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">plus their value as a source,</font>

241
00:11:34,330 --> 00:11:37,920
<font size="20" color="#000000"><b><font size="15"><font color="#1f1f32">Pretty Good</font></font></b></font>

242
00:11:35,340 --> 00:11:37,920
<font size="20" color="#000000"><b><font size="15"><font color="#1f1f32">Impressive</font></font></b></font>

243
00:11:35,400 --> 00:11:37,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">determines whether 
they're korokke or not.</font>

244
00:11:36,340 --> 00:11:37,920
<font size="20" color="#000000"><b><font size="12"><font color="#1f1f32">Super Rare</font></font></b></font>

245
00:11:37,090 --> 00:11:37,920
<font size="20" color="#000000"><b><font size="8"><font color="#1f1f32">Based on 
overall combined
 circumstances 
such as how 
the organizations
 are linked.</font></font></b></font>

246
00:11:37,920 --> 00:11:41,880
<font size="20" color="#000000"><b><font color="#303030">Let's build a <font color="#ea3574">fun, 
cheerful <font color="#303030">workplace together!</font></font></font></b></font>

247
00:11:37,920 --> 00:11:41,880
<font size="20" color="#000000"><b><font color="#dffedf">Stop harassment!</font></b></font>

248
00:11:38,160 --> 00:11:41,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's an inherent risk to torturing.</font>

249
00:11:41,880 --> 00:11:45,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A certain number of accidents 
outside of korokke cases is expected.</font>

250
00:11:45,920 --> 00:11:46,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's just...</font>

251
00:11:46,870 --> 00:11:51,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">we lose some organs and information 
that could be converted into cash.</font>

252
00:11:51,030 --> 00:11:52,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see.</font>

253
00:11:52,280 --> 00:11:53,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry.</font>

254
00:12:01,000 --> 00:12:01,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks.</font>

255
00:12:02,400 --> 00:12:04,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Have they calmed down?</font>

256
00:12:05,920 --> 00:12:08,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">More or less. I'm sure they'll be fine.</font>

257
00:12:09,310 --> 00:12:10,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You seem laid-back about it.</font>

258
00:12:11,310 --> 00:12:12,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did you say anything to them?</font>

259
00:12:12,870 --> 00:12:15,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I did give them a bit of a scolding,</font>

260
00:12:15,690 --> 00:12:18,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but those two understand 
what's important,</font>

261
00:12:18,400 --> 00:12:20,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so I didn't yell at them.</font>

262
00:12:20,760 --> 00:12:22,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, hearing it from a guy</font>

263
00:12:22,550 --> 00:12:25,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">who can't always keep his 
emotions in check around scum</font>

264
00:12:25,520 --> 00:12:27,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">wouldn't be very convincing, anyway.</font>

265
00:12:27,750 --> 00:12:29,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

266
00:12:29,000 --> 00:12:31,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How to handle the aftermath 
in times like that</font>

267
00:12:31,560 --> 00:12:34,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">is a lesson I learned 
from watching you, though.</font>

268
00:12:34,070 --> 00:12:35,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Dunno anything about that.</font>

269
00:12:35,240 --> 00:12:36,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

270
00:12:39,310 --> 00:12:41,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It still bothers you?</font>

271
00:12:41,740 --> 00:12:43,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A little.</font>

272
00:12:43,240 --> 00:12:44,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A bit.</font>

273
00:12:44,440 --> 00:12:46,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Noe-chan is handling it for you, right?</font>

274
00:12:46,930 --> 00:12:48,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's...</font>

275
00:12:48,240 --> 00:12:50,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">...true, but...</font>

276
00:12:50,460 --> 00:12:55,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Could it be that you 
regret killing your target?</font>

277
00:12:55,800 --> 00:12:57,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, not in the slightest.</font>

278
00:12:57,730 --> 00:13:01,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Those who come here are criminals 
for whom death is too light a punishment.</font>

279
00:13:01,630 --> 00:13:03,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're so stoic.</font>

280
00:13:04,260 --> 00:13:06,380
<font size="20" color="#000000"><b><font size="12"><font color="#ecedf8">Would you like to talk about your workplace worries?</font></font></b></font>

281
00:13:04,260 --> 00:13:06,380
<font size="20" color="#000000"><b><font size="12"><font color="#ecedf8">Don't take it all on alone. Come and give us a try.</font></font></b></font>

282
00:13:04,260 --> 00:13:06,380
<font size="20" color="#000000"><font size="12"><b><font color="#e0c0b2">Free consultations</font></b></font></font>

283
00:13:06,560 --> 00:13:09,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just when they'd started trusting 
us with so many things...</font>

284
00:13:09,870 --> 00:13:11,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">...we made a mistake like that.</font>

285
00:13:11,600 --> 00:13:13,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I just feel so bad.</font>

286
00:13:14,490 --> 00:13:18,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even careful veterans can 
have this kind of accident,</font>

287
00:13:18,090 --> 00:13:20,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so I don't think you need 
to worry so much.</font>

288
00:13:20,670 --> 00:13:22,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Von-san...</font>

289
00:13:22,050 --> 00:13:23,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Though...</font>

290
00:13:23,340 --> 00:13:27,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I will be putting in a claim for 
the organs that are no longer viable!</font>

291
00:13:27,580 --> 00:13:28,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?!</font>

292
00:13:29,140 --> 00:13:32,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wh-Where should I go to donate them?</font>

293
00:13:32,000 --> 00:13:34,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-If it's something I have two of...</font>

294
00:13:34,120 --> 00:13:35,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No need. No need at all.</font>

295
00:13:36,000 --> 00:13:39,920
<font size="20" color="#000000"><font face="Times New Roman"><b>{\an7}<font color="#de4a5b">Torture <font color="#4b4b4b">builds a sustainable society</font></font></b></font></font>

296
00:13:36,040 --> 00:13:39,920
<font size="20" color="#000000"><font face="Times New Roman"><b>{\an8}<font color="#de4a5b">Give the villains 
the <font color="#9a4f59">iron hammer</font></font></b></font></font>

297
00:13:37,090 --> 00:13:39,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Isn't holding lives in your hands scary?</font>

298
00:13:40,090 --> 00:13:43,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you two have something you believe in?</font>

299
00:13:43,790 --> 00:13:47,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It is a little scary. But...</font>

300
00:13:47,550 --> 00:13:49,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We can't stay scared.</font>

301
00:13:50,080 --> 00:13:52,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Because this is something 
we decided to do ourselves.</font>

302
00:13:52,840 --> 00:13:56,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">As for things I believe in... 
Maybe the work itself?</font>

303
00:13:56,240 --> 00:13:57,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And Siu-san and the others?</font>

304
00:13:57,730 --> 00:13:59,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And you, too, Hugh.</font>

305
00:13:59,810 --> 00:14:01,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And I believe in you.</font>

306
00:14:02,680 --> 00:14:05,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is that so? I'm glad.</font>

307
00:14:05,160 --> 00:14:08,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You two... will be just fine.</font>

308
00:14:09,440 --> 00:14:10,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is it true, Von?</font>

309
00:14:12,030 --> 00:14:14,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I heard you're quitting torturing.</font>

310
00:14:14,740 --> 00:14:17,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah. I'm not suited to it.</font>

311
00:14:17,700 --> 00:14:19,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Unlike the two of you.</font>

312
00:14:19,330 --> 00:14:20,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Really?</font>

313
00:14:20,400 --> 00:14:21,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, really.</font>

314
00:14:22,080 --> 00:14:24,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You two feel that it's worthwhile,</font>

315
00:14:24,480 --> 00:14:26,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and you have things 
you believe in, right?</font>

316
00:14:27,360 --> 00:14:31,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You have something to help you overcome 
the dissonance of hurting people.</font>

317
00:14:31,950 --> 00:14:35,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think torture is necessary. 
I admired it, and that's why I started.</font>

318
00:14:36,420 --> 00:14:38,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But with vague feelings like that...</font>

319
00:14:38,930 --> 00:14:42,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I haven't been able to fully 
believe in what I have to do.</font>

320
00:14:44,200 --> 00:14:45,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Really?</font>

321
00:14:46,190 --> 00:14:48,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, it'll feel a little lonely.</font>

322
00:14:49,130 --> 00:14:50,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And so! And so!</font>

323
00:14:53,720 --> 00:14:56,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm going to start working 
as a scrap handler!</font>

324
00:14:56,660 --> 00:15:00,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Turning crimes and lives into money 
is so much easier, don't you think?</font>

325
00:15:00,370 --> 00:15:03,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not using vague ideas 
to prop myself up anymore!</font>

326
00:15:03,930 --> 00:15:07,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll take responsibility for the part 
that comes after the torture!</font>

327
00:15:07,280 --> 00:15:10,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">For acting all sensitive, 
you're certainly bold.</font>

328
00:15:10,640 --> 00:15:12,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And what are those sunglasses for?</font>

329
00:15:12,530 --> 00:15:15,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll have to connect 
with terrifying customers,</font>

330
00:15:15,580 --> 00:15:17,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so they're, like... a disguise?</font>

331
00:15:17,480 --> 00:15:19,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're just too shrewd.</font>

332
00:15:23,800 --> 00:15:26,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Von-san was super nice 
yesterday, wasn't he?</font>

333
00:15:26,790 --> 00:15:27,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right?</font>

334
00:15:28,000 --> 00:15:28,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

335
00:15:29,200 --> 00:15:30,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just as he was leaving...</font>

336
00:15:31,410 --> 00:15:35,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You two just believe in yourselves 
and keep working hard, okay?</font>

337
00:15:37,160 --> 00:15:39,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">...was what he said to us.</font>

338
00:15:39,680 --> 00:15:41,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It was very encouraging.</font>

339
00:15:41,920 --> 00:15:45,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, numbskulls, don't let him fool you.</font>

340
00:15:45,150 --> 00:15:49,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When Von-san handles the aftermath of 
irregularities, he gets to name his price.</font>

341
00:15:49,330 --> 00:15:53,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He was being nice to you because 
he was going to make a lot more money.</font>

342
00:15:53,840 --> 00:15:56,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks for your business!</font>

343
00:15:56,280 --> 00:15:57,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What kind of person does that?</font>

344
00:16:01,180 --> 00:16:03,650
<font size="20" color="#000000"><b><font size="35"><font color="#050505">{\an9}Lecture Room F</font></font></b></font>

345
00:16:01,800 --> 00:16:03,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mike-san, long time no see!</font>

346
00:16:03,650 --> 00:16:05,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you looking for material again?</font>

347
00:16:05,180 --> 00:16:06,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's been a while!</font>

348
00:16:06,580 --> 00:16:09,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Both looking for material 
and studying, I guess.</font>

349
00:16:09,990 --> 00:16:13,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you're coming to the lecture, 
Russ-kun, does that mean...</font>

350
00:16:13,110 --> 00:16:15,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">you've taken an interest in torture?</font>

351
00:16:15,080 --> 00:16:16,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Want to come to our company?</font>

352
00:16:16,340 --> 00:16:17,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think I'll pass.</font>

353
00:16:18,120 --> 00:16:20,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I just came because I had nothing 
to do and it's interesting.</font>

354
00:16:20,860 --> 00:16:22,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's too bad.</font>

355
00:16:22,370 --> 00:16:26,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When you're all here,
things are so lively. It's nice.</font>

356
00:16:26,270 --> 00:16:28,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's usually just me and Hugh-kun.</font>

357
00:16:28,690 --> 00:16:31,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I didn't know there were classes 
with this few students in them.</font>

358
00:16:31,550 --> 00:16:33,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even when there are more,</font>

359
00:16:33,380 --> 00:16:36,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">they're just dabbling or 
hoping for easy credits.</font>

360
00:16:36,310 --> 00:16:39,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hugh-kun is the only one I can 
have meaningful discussions with.</font>

361
00:16:40,480 --> 00:16:41,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's that bad?</font>

362
00:16:43,910 --> 00:16:48,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mike-kun, you work at the same 
place as Hugh-kun, right?</font>

363
00:16:48,390 --> 00:16:49,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, sir!</font>

364
00:16:49,160 --> 00:16:51,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Spirytus takes very good care of us!</font>

365
00:16:51,690 --> 00:16:53,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is torturing fun?</font>

366
00:16:53,900 --> 00:16:56,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes! Lots of fun!</font>

367
00:16:56,550 --> 00:16:58,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What a great smile.</i></font>

368
00:16:58,100 --> 00:17:01,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Given the current rules 
and laws around torture,</font>

369
00:17:01,120 --> 00:17:03,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">is there anything 
you're dissatisfied with?</font>

370
00:17:03,730 --> 00:17:07,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There are a few things 
I wish were a little different,</font>

371
00:17:07,860 --> 00:17:11,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but there's nothing we can do about 
things that are already decided.</font>

372
00:17:11,050 --> 00:17:17,220
<font size="20" color="#000000">{\an7}<b><font face="Comic Sans MS"><font color="#211923">HEH HEH HEH</font></font></b></font>

373
00:17:11,470 --> 00:17:15,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think doing everything I can 
within those lines is the real thrill!</font>

374
00:17:15,160 --> 00:17:17,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How very stalwart of you.</font>

375
00:17:17,390 --> 00:17:20,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hugh-kun, unlike Mike-kun,</font>

376
00:17:20,450 --> 00:17:23,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">you think there's a need to 
change some of the rules, right?</font>

377
00:17:23,750 --> 00:17:24,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, sir.</font>

378
00:17:24,930 --> 00:17:27,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I feel that with the 
application of more pain,</font>

379
00:17:27,840 --> 00:17:29,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">much more information could be extracted.</font>

380
00:17:29,800 --> 00:17:32,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You are quite stalwart, as well.</font>

381
00:17:32,640 --> 00:17:37,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your sense of justice is very valuable, 
but you mustn't go too far.</font>

382
00:17:37,770 --> 00:17:41,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But there are truly irredeemable 
villains among them.</font>

383
00:17:41,520 --> 00:17:43,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I do understand how you feel.</font>

384
00:17:44,520 --> 00:17:47,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">After all, I worked as a torturer, too.</font>

385
00:17:49,920 --> 00:17:50,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

386
00:17:51,000 --> 00:17:53,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You were a torturer?!</font>

387
00:17:53,380 --> 00:17:55,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Didn't I mention it?</font>

388
00:17:55,160 --> 00:17:57,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Despite how I look, long ago, 
I was quite in-demand!</font>

389
00:17:57,940 --> 00:17:59,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wow.</font>

390
00:18:00,260 --> 00:18:02,680
<font size="20" color="#000000"><b><font size="35"><font color="#050505">{\an9}Lecture Room F</font></font></b></font>

391
00:18:01,160 --> 00:18:05,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do the two of you intend 
to continue as torturers?</font>

392
00:18:05,760 --> 00:18:10,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, I'm still planning to 
continue in two professions.</font>

393
00:18:10,800 --> 00:18:13,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If I think about it in terms 
of a future career,</font>

394
00:18:13,130 --> 00:18:15,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm a little uncertain.</font>

395
00:18:15,760 --> 00:18:18,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I love my current work and workplace,</font>

396
00:18:18,480 --> 00:18:23,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and I'm thinking about continuing 
in work somehow related to torture.</font>

397
00:18:23,950 --> 00:18:27,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I'm not certain about what 
I should be aiming for yet.</font>

398
00:18:27,640 --> 00:18:29,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In that case, Hugh-kun,</font>

399
00:18:30,370 --> 00:18:33,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">you might as well aim for 
the top, don't you think?</font>

400
00:18:33,110 --> 00:18:33,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The top?</font>

401
00:18:33,920 --> 00:18:38,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I believe your thoughts about 
the rules that should be changed</font>

402
00:18:38,400 --> 00:18:43,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">would do well in the Torture Association, 
a group above the workers on the ground.</font>

403
00:18:43,350 --> 00:18:45,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, yeah, that could be a good fit for you.</font>

404
00:18:47,960 --> 00:18:50,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'd never even considered that.</font>

405
00:18:50,270 --> 00:18:52,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sounds good. You'd be good at it.</font>

406
00:18:52,860 --> 00:18:53,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

407
00:18:53,890 --> 00:18:57,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But does that mean I won't be 
able to work with you anymore?</font>

408
00:18:57,790 --> 00:18:59,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? Oh, no!</font>

409
00:19:00,610 --> 00:19:03,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want to cheer you on, 
but I'd hate that!</font>

410
00:19:03,710 --> 00:19:05,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It'd make me feel lonely, too!</font>

411
00:19:05,680 --> 00:19:08,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It wouldn't happen right away.</font>

412
00:19:08,390 --> 00:19:10,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And gaining experience 
is very important,</font>

413
00:19:10,340 --> 00:19:12,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so he should continue working for now.</font>

414
00:19:13,290 --> 00:19:15,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Yay!</font>

415
00:19:13,290 --> 00:19:15,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What a relief!</font>

416
00:19:15,040 --> 00:19:17,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now, let's continue the lesson.</font>

417
00:19:17,280 --> 00:19:18,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, sir.</font>

418
00:19:23,440 --> 00:19:27,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can't use this on a Class 3 
torture target, can you?</font>

419
00:19:27,520 --> 00:19:28,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're right.</font>

420
00:19:28,690 --> 00:19:31,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? If you check it against
 that law from earlier,</font>

421
00:19:31,420 --> 00:19:33,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">it can be used on some of them, right?</font>

422
00:19:34,140 --> 00:19:36,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Such an approach exists?!</font>

423
00:19:36,920 --> 00:19:39,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stop looking at me like 
I'm some kind of genius.</font>

424
00:19:39,760 --> 00:19:41,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It was just a fluke.</font>

425
00:19:41,070 --> 00:19:44,910
<font size="20" color="#000000"><b><font size="35"><font color="#20110b">{\an9}Lecture Room F</font></font></b></font>

426
00:19:42,950 --> 00:19:44,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you for today.</font>

427
00:19:44,910 --> 00:19:45,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks.</font>

428
00:19:45,720 --> 00:19:47,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is it all right if I come again?</font>

429
00:19:48,780 --> 00:19:50,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're welcome to.</font>

430
00:19:50,100 --> 00:19:54,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please give my regards to everyone 
at Spirytus and to Hera.</font>

431
00:19:54,410 --> 00:19:55,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We will!</font>

432
00:19:57,870 --> 00:19:58,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

433
00:19:58,610 --> 00:20:02,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wonder how the professor 
knows Hera-san's name.</font>

434
00:20:02,130 --> 00:20:05,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Maybe it's because he's famous 
as the head of Spirytus?</font>

435
00:20:11,000 --> 00:20:13,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Today was fun, wasn't it?</font>

436
00:20:13,000 --> 00:20:15,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah. Thanks for coming with me.</font>

437
00:20:15,810 --> 00:20:19,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, thank you for inviting me.</font>

438
00:20:19,220 --> 00:20:22,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's great that you found 
something you can call a goal.</font>

439
00:20:22,900 --> 00:20:24,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I suppose so.</font>

440
00:20:24,400 --> 00:20:25,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hugh?</font>

441
00:20:25,530 --> 00:20:27,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If I join the Torture Association,</font>

442
00:20:27,550 --> 00:20:31,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I won't be able to work 
with everyone anymore.</font>

443
00:20:31,350 --> 00:20:33,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thinking about that makes me sad.</font>

444
00:20:33,730 --> 00:20:35,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It makes me sad, too.</font>

445
00:20:35,660 --> 00:20:38,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I think it'd make me sadder if you</font>

446
00:20:38,120 --> 00:20:41,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">gave up the goal you 
just found for yourself.</font>

447
00:20:41,620 --> 00:20:42,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mike-kun...</font>

448
00:20:43,560 --> 00:20:47,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want you to do the 
things you want to do!</font>

449
00:20:48,770 --> 00:20:52,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So, while you're learning 
all kinds of things at Spirytus,</font>

450
00:20:52,310 --> 00:20:54,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">you should find the thing you want to do.</font>

451
00:20:55,230 --> 00:20:56,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're right.</font>

452
00:20:56,800 --> 00:20:58,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll think about it and try looking!</font>

453
00:20:58,800 --> 00:21:00,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's the spirit!</font>

454
00:21:00,280 --> 00:21:04,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll both keep working hard 
toward our goals together!</font>

455
00:21:05,140 --> 00:21:07,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah. Let's give it our best!</font>

456
00:21:13,320 --> 00:21:14,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Really?</font>

457
00:21:15,100 --> 00:21:18,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Aiming for the Torture 
Association, are you?</font>

458
00:21:18,000 --> 00:21:20,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, that sounds wonderful!</font>

459
00:21:20,290 --> 00:21:22,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You'll basically continue to 
do what you've been doing,</font>

460
00:21:22,610 --> 00:21:25,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but I'll assist you so that you'll have 
that option available to you.</font>

461
00:21:25,760 --> 00:21:27,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you so much!</font>

462
00:21:27,960 --> 00:21:30,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Still, the professor who 
recommended it to you</font>

463
00:21:30,940 --> 00:21:33,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">must have quite the eye for talent!</font>

464
00:21:34,000 --> 00:21:35,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's his name?</font>

465
00:21:35,250 --> 00:21:38,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, he's called Professor Summon.</font>

466
00:21:40,440 --> 00:21:41,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you okay?!</font>

467
00:21:41,340 --> 00:21:43,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He hasn't done anything 
horrible to you, has he?!</font>

468
00:21:43,680 --> 00:21:46,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's always smiling. 
He's a very nice person.</font>

469
00:21:46,440 --> 00:21:47,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Truly?</font>

470
00:21:47,850 --> 00:21:49,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Y-Yes.</font>

471
00:21:49,390 --> 00:21:52,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is Professor Summon someone scary?</font>

472
00:21:52,040 --> 00:21:53,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who is he?</font>

473
00:21:53,000 --> 00:21:55,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh. He's Hera's...</font>

474
00:21:55,240 --> 00:21:55,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">teacher.</font>

475
00:21:55,840 --> 00:21:58,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}I never imagined I'd connect 
with him like this!</font>

476
00:21:56,440 --> 00:21:58,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?!</font>

477
00:21:58,950 --> 00:22:00,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The way Hera-san is reacting...</font>

478
00:22:00,880 --> 00:22:03,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What kind of person is Professor Summon?</font>

479
00:22:04,410 --> 00:22:05,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Gulp.</font>

480
00:22:05,690 --> 00:22:07,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, stop making such a fuss.</font>

481
00:22:38,210 --> 00:22:45,590
<font size="20" color="#000000"><font size="12"><b><font color="#eff0f3">{\an9}Translator:
Timer:
Editor:
Quality Control:
Final Quality Control:</font></b></font></font>

482
00:22:38,210 --> 00:22:45,590
